{"id": "ChIJw7m3ara-woARlTMkaqt8Pkc", "rating": 4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_VERY_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 134, "displayName": {"text": "Vivienne Westwood Los Angeles", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJw7m3ara-woARlTMkaqt8Pkc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKQ1lWazJXV1poV1hnNFMzRnhhRU5mTWtsWVIyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I went yesterday knowing what I wanted but I also left knowing what I’ll come back for ! Thank you so much to Zoey for helping me they’re the GOAT!!! I wanted to try on some clothes and they asked me if I wanted to try anything else on and they suprised me with a beautiful long sleeve shirt matched with a corset ! I also love how they took the boots that I was wearing into consideration of the outfit overall! Their styling was AMAZING!! And they were super super helpful and sweet ! There was another employee who I forgot the name of but he was helping me at first but went on break for a bit but he was also super kind in helping me pick out a wallet!! Honestly everyone in that store really cared for the customers! I will be coming back for some of the clothes I tried on!! >:)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I went yesterday knowing what I wanted but I also left knowing what I’ll come back for ! Thank you so much to Zoey for helping me they’re the GOAT!!! I wanted to try on some clothes and they asked me if I wanted to try anything else on and they suprised me with a beautiful long sleeve shirt matched with a corset ! I also love how they took the boots that I was wearing into consideration of the outfit overall! Their styling was AMAZING!! And they were super super helpful and sweet ! There was another employee who I forgot the name of but he was helping me at first but went on break for a bit but he was also super kind in helping me pick out a wallet!! Honestly everyone in that store really cared for the customers! I will be coming back for some of the clothes I tried on!! >:)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Elizabeth Engeda", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117258895179121301483/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuVW267bGI5be7SxJXZUE_2ZuIUWCB058cgyXZrhlE5WXWZFdMHA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-02T17:29:51.538459657Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKQ1lWazJXV1poV1hnNFMzRnhhRU5mTWtsWVIyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKQ1lWazJXV1poV1hnNFMzRnhhRU5mTWtsWVIyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2beb66ab7b9c3:0x473e7cab6a243395"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw7m3ara-woARlTMkaqt8Pkc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paNFgwVlRPRlpWUlhwaE9HUnNjM0ZLUm1KeVRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Finally made the pilgrimage to visit this store considering how far my GF and I live and we had a pleasant experience. the staff were friendly, very helpful, and knowledgeable. I’m very happy with the impulse purchase i made that day haha", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Finally made the pilgrimage to visit this store considering how far my GF and I live and we had a pleasant experience. the staff were friendly, very helpful, and knowledgeable. I’m very happy with the impulse purchase i made that day haha", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nicholas Sanchez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110364614520536665612/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_SCY8neoy2oUBDyukDFgsXlo_3gim1TY1UDjClpJFN2S-44Qj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-08T07:44:01.016681350Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paNFgwVlRPRlpWUlhwaE9HUnNjM0ZLUm1KeVRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paNFgwVlRPRlpWUlhwaE9HUnNjM0ZLUm1KeVRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2beb66ab7b9c3:0x473e7cab6a243395"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw7m3ara-woARlTMkaqt8Pkc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BemJEWXdRa2hsUjFrdFltWXpUa0YwY1VveFJWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I visited the L.A. location and had such a great time shopping during my visit! Jared was incredibly helpful and had amazing style insight when helping me decide what to buy. I can’t wait to come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I visited the L.A. location and had such a great time shopping during my visit! Jared was incredibly helpful and had amazing style insight when helping me decide what to buy. I can’t wait to come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sumaya", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112956227754862618841/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8VBjeybTumZ58oi5Rs9s3qLm2DBCnTFiLhzOVHNUzY2MwUauk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-05T19:08:20.401339170Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BemJEWXdRa2hsUjFrdFltWXpUa0YwY1VveFJWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BemJEWXdRa2hsUjFrdFltWXpUa0YwY1VveFJWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2beb66ab7b9c3:0x473e7cab6a243395"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw7m3ara-woARlTMkaqt8Pkc/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3OUlfRmJnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Maybe the best designer brand, everything literally EVERYTHING in here is well made, well designed, beautiful, and PERFECT. Vivienne Westwood is not afraid of actually interesting and unique design and I love that. It's extremely hard not to just throw out all of your money here. Do not be afraid of that price tag because unlike a lot of the other brands these pieces are 100% worth it! This store itself is also very cool the way it's set up and looks, one of my favorite places in the fashion section of LA, especially thank you to Xavier and Nicky (hope I got those names right) for helping me in finding the absolute PERFECT garment to take home. This is a store everyone needs to experience at least once", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Maybe the best designer brand, everything literally EVERYTHING in here is well made, well designed, beautiful, and PERFECT. Vivienne Westwood is not afraid of actually interesting and unique design and I love that. It's extremely hard not to just throw out all of your money here. Do not be afraid of that price tag because unlike a lot of the other brands these pieces are 100% worth it! This store itself is also very cool the way it's set up and looks, one of my favorite places in the fashion section of LA, especially thank you to Xavier and Nicky (hope I got those names right) for helping me in finding the absolute PERFECT garment to take home. This is a store everyone needs to experience at least once", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chase E", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104798501964289468910/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXemk15XULABX32qIxLlnOju0BGBS5VkYDz17h7bbX51ugg8-FR=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2024-08-13T05:16:27.044088Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3OUlfRmJnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM3OUlfRmJnEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2beb66ab7b9c3:0x473e7cab6a243395"}, {"name": "places/ChIJw7m3ara-woARlTMkaqt8Pkc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wQ1RrdFRTRjgwT1ZOTE9HNWFNalJwVGtscVEzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": 